Reported-by: Joseph Salisbury <joseph.salisbury@canonical.com>
Reported-and-tested-by: Stephen Thirlwall <sdt@dr.com>
Signed-off-by: Greg Kroah-Hartman <gregkh@linuxfoundation.org>
